<div id="caseText"><p><strong>Harvey Nichols</strong></p><p>We created a brand new ecommerce system for Harvey Nichols Christmas hampers in 2004 and have augmented it with new features in 2005.</p><p>The new system included a bespoke sales admin system for managing online/telephone orders, stock and deliveries, as well as the facility to report on sales.</p><p>The front end was completely redesigned with an intuitive and simple shopping process, resulting in a significant increase in the volume and value of orders.</p><p>As lead digital agency we redesigned the careers section and created email templates and competition pages for Harvey Nichols. The careers section allows visitors to apply online and register for updates.</p><p>The site uses our content management system and has achieved top rankings on Google and other major search engines for hamper-related search terms.</p><p><a target="_blank" href="http://www.harveynichols.com">http://www.harveynichols.com</a></p></div>
